#CAMERA 9
#phrase Elder  1
The Middle Mountains are dangerous nowadays, though a while ago it was quite different. Humans used to have an understanding with the Lizards who live there. They even put a sign of peace on their altar to show the way was open  - a big Shell.
#ANIMATION 32
#CAMERA 7
#phrase Elder  2
But a short time ago the Shell disappeared - and the Middle Mountains became dangerous again!
